{"tid":2063104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個個都講35+之後點 但係好少人講唔夠35+可以點","createTime":"2020-06-13T15:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T06:23:16.000Z","uid":40431,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"84dfcbe089f91dc8672deb2b4502d449dd12e385","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申先，有35+一定係最好，無論如何都盡力搏一搏</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係如果最後差少少，可能有30席甚至再差啲得10席咁，入咗去嗰啲人可以做咩？<br />\n唔夠35+可以係因為我哋配票唔夠對家好，可以係投票結果出完中共先DQ。<br />\n<br />\n感覺上好多討論都係話35+之後點否決政府議案，或者如果未選已經DQ晒就杯葛選舉。<br />\n但係如果中共俾你投到35+，之後先搵藉口DQ到唔夠數呢？<br />\n國際線嘅彈藥一定有，但係國際線係人哋出聲唔係我哋主導，問題係議員可以做乜？<br />\n老實講，到時入到議會嘅人如果又係好似而家嘅泛民咁都係冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以話我放負，不過我覺得現實少少討論多啲都冇壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617ca1f433475055d94c8b4ee28a5de2b7c4c9b1","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"622d24f748a23de1a69aad67478e5875295f7eb3","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffa878888b5bf9d6b55519e2ae7d1b3e5dc94d0","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:41:19.000Z","msg":"一齊諗吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23554e540c24a2770b34c1a730240c23aeae7fd","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:42:04.000Z","msg":"負評都可以講吓點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0102e9cff945eb577a202943c189655dcdc358","tid":2063104,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"少人講係因為個個心知就算有35+都冇咩可以點"},{"pid":"9c337ddcfcec87a552ef9896979ea786ddedf976","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"一齊討論吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7ee83cbe23974c6dade32774282c6a8b053d25","tid":2063104,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"咪好似依家咁<br />\n大口狗繼續做主席"},{"pid":"d6c719bb13d0573d356fe71ddc04af4a0110194b","tid":2063104,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"五毛最怕35+有權修改法例，日日玩分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6192c63a55292ba5dff8e75979610f053e72afad","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d6c719bb13d0573d356fe71ddc04af4a0110194b","tid":2063104,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"五毛最怕35+有權修改法例，日日玩分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"你都幾好笑<br />\n邊個而家夠膽講一定可以35+呀<br />\n做乜都好都要諗定贏嘅話點樣輸嘅話點樣啦<br />\n去遊行都要諗定點退啦<br />\n如果唔夠數，咁係掟嘢定總辭定點呀<br />\n連諗遠啲都唔肯，唔通好似而家咁一係投反對票做樣一係俾人趕晒出去就算呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd50bc6631fff85a656556e389025b5eca2a072","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b7ee83cbe23974c6dade32774282c6a8b053d25","tid":2063104,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"咪好似依家咁<br />\n大口狗繼續做主席"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"大口狗繼續做主席<br />\n但係抗爭手法上都可以變<br />\n人哋外國玩到可以掟tear gas<br />\n香港連臭魚都未掟"},{"pid":"48651837f8cfd099722869122af878937f9e5297","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c495a514b4dfa6273bab5b23780e73ff78ec395","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7352edaea3ba95a02e03988fcec0d38b636e61c1","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea0102e9cff945eb577a202943c189655dcdc358","tid":2063104,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"少人講係因為個個心知就算有35+都冇咩可以點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:09:52.000Z","msg":"如果真係有35+ 起碼有控制議會嘅權力<br />\n否決晒政府提出嘅法案都好呀"},{"pid":"f1c8ea25adcc44389a8bee921c261416b8ce463b","tid":2063104,"uid":143031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"如果少過35, 但係30+, 會唔會有可能係某D議案進行分組點票可以否決到?"},{"pid":"f6149cc054f105e79e6636d2049532092fbce077","tid":2063104,"uid":276090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:18:01.000Z","msg":"到左今時今日～ 我要35+只係等睇中共發狂～ 唔夠咪即係而家咁～ 就算夠35+都冇興趣理之後點～  只要中共見到35+ 佢就唔會安心～ 根本唔洗有plan中共都會柒出黎～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f91b577819297b8997a3e224572f1c4c9c15a3","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1c8ea25adcc44389a8bee921c261416b8ce463b","tid":2063104,"uid":143031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"如果少過35, 但係30+, 會唔會有可能係某D議案進行分組點票可以否決到?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"泛民喺之前幾屆，甚至DQ之前都有分組否決權<br />\n可以話好過冇，否決到啲修正案或者私人提出嘅法案<br />\n但係同時都只可以否決到呢啲，想通過自己嘢或者改議事規則都係做唔到"},{"pid":"b07be453ad6051929ea7693d7f616a43554b8184","tid":2063104,"uid":143031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32f91b577819297b8997a3e224572f1c4c9c15a3","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1c8ea25adcc44389a8bee921c261416b8ce463b","tid":2063104,"uid":143031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"如果少過35, 但係30+, 會唔會有可能係某D議案進行分組點票可以否決到?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"泛民喺之前幾屆，甚至DQ之前都有分組否決權<br />\n可以話好過冇，否決到啲修正案或者私人提出嘅法案<br />\n但係同時都只可以否決到呢啲，想通過自己嘢或者改議事規則都係做唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"參照維基，原來都係地區直選過半即18席就可以否決呢類議案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過認同你講既，都係有好過冇既功能。<br />\n<br />\n要否決政府提案，真係非35+不可<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83#%E5%88%86%E7%B5%84%E9%BB%9E%E7%A5%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%23%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25B5%2584%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%25A5%25A8&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=eb13c895\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83#%E5%88%86%E7%B5%84%E9%BB%9E%E7%A5%A8</a><br />\n<em>《基本法》附件二規定，由議員個人提出的法案（私人條例草案）、議案和對政府法案（包括財政預算案）的修正案，表決時須以分組點票方式點算，要同時得到地區直選及功能界別分別過半數出席議員贊成（2004年第三屆立法會之前，選舉委員會議員與地區直選議員作同一組），議案才獲通過[19]。</em>"},{"pid":"f7817c80a877f1bb5af1611720b7813f0e77836a","tid":2063104,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"4年後繼續投"},{"pid":"3eb961a28dd89c88d8b2ae5451592071b7099416","tid":2063104,"uid":37860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"參考上屆熱狗5區公投<br />\n一達唔到目標就直接跳票"},{"pid":"664f94a88624b561bd2d97b918dbeca325126db8","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3eb961a28dd89c88d8b2ae5451592071b7099416","tid":2063104,"uid":37860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"參考上屆熱狗5區公投<br />\n一達唔到目標就直接跳票"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:46:22.000Z","msg":"搞變相公投都只係民意表態<br />\n但係如果講到點運用個議席或者喺議會做啲咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f15b7152f8a8bc8b040e8da6080cbfc5e230d7f","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38b7820f80497cc1534ed94196f912138cb047f","tid":2063104,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:49:07.000Z","msg":"討論吓都好呀 過多幾個月就係喇"},{"pid":"df75d1fa8a36a4509339cc483d5de881529c0fe6","tid":2063104,"uid":338459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T18:19:27.000Z","msg":"副本任務，一試無妨<br />\n失敗情況唔會差咗，一向都差<br />\n但成功咗可以開心一陣，無錯係一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf24f0235f8f65f6dd20784107dd434fe72a9a87","tid":2063104,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T19:38:22.000Z","msg":"35+fail左<br />\n基本上立會同而家無分別，最多只會係突襲點人數同迫佢下下投票都要齊人<br />\n<br />\n心態上好多人會覺得香港冇撚得救，一心移民，爭在係即走定係揾夠錢退休先走，因為呢一次係民意反彈最大嘅時候，如果咁都選唔到黎緊唔使浪費心機。"}]}